title: O'Neill - Don't Get Burned!
description:
Don't Get Burned! PROTECTION FROM THE ELEMENTS. http://www.oneill.com/wetsuits/produc...
O'Neill offers five distinct series of UV protection product to keep you covered. The highly technical O'Zone Series (8oz Nylon/Spandex) is designed for extended sessions in tropical sun. The 24-7 is our loose-fit series (5oz Nylon/Spandex Composite). It is breathable and protects against sun fatigue in and out of the water. The versatile Skins and Basic Skins Series offers UV and rash protection in a wide variety of styles. Thinskins is perfect for the performance minded athlete who needs a little core warmth.
